# Summary
This documentation page explains how to implement Amplitude's Web Experiment by adding a script to a website's `<head>` element, covering synchronous and asynchronous implementation options with anti-flicker snippets, third-party CDP integrations, CMS support (WordPress and Shopify), and tag manager implementation considerations.

